column2: "You're open!"
"...damn!"
"Ugh... That chipped my blade..."
"...but it wasn't for nothing."
"Curse you!"

"That guy was pretty tough.
<%me>, are you alright?"
"You managed to hold your own. Nice work."
"But what was he after? You, or that thing you're holding?"

"...a weird sound?
No, I didn't hear anything like that."
"Me neither..."
"Still no sound readings in the data."
"We can think about it once we're back in the lobby. Might as well head back now."
"You got the data you were after, right, Rogio?"
"Yes. This should be sufficient."
"But why do you know the details of the quest?"
"A good mentor always looks after his pupil."
"You made me look it up."
"Don't blow my cover. Anyway, let's head back."
"エコーをパートナーとして呼べるようになりました。"
"Acquired [Broken Weapon/Axis]"
"The frozen origin"
"第２章 不気味なナベリウス"
